OL,3,CTwo men to be sentenced over #4.75
OL,4,Cmillion gold toilet heist
OL,6,FTwo men will be sentenced over the
OL,7,Ftheft of a #4.75 million gold toilet
OL,8,Ffrom Blenheim Palace.
OL,10,FThe fully-functioning 18-carat gold
OL,11,Ftoilet, which had been installed as an
OL,12,Fartwork at the Oxfordshire country
OL,13,Fhouse where Sir Winston Churchill was
OL,14,Fborn, was stolen in a raid in the
OL,15,Fearly hours of September 14 2019.
OL,17,FThe distinctive toilet, the star
OL,18,Fattraction in an exhibition at the
OL,19,Fproperty, is believed to have been
OL,20,Fbroken up and disposed of after it was
OL,21,Ftaken.
