OL,6,FJurors at Oxford Crown Court found
OL,7,FMichael Jones, 39, guilty of burglary
OL,8,Fafter a trial.
OL,10,FJames Sheen, 40, from Wellingborough,
OL,11,FNorthamptonshire, had already admitted
OL,12,Fburglary at the same court.
OL,14,FHe also pleaded guilty to transferring
OL,15,Fcriminal property and conspiracy to
OL,16,Ftransfer criminal property.
