OL,6,FSheen is serving a 17-year sentence
OL,7,Ffor a string of thefts, including
OL,8,F#400,000 worth of tractors and high-
OL,9,Fvalue trophies from the National Horse
OL,10,FRacing Museum in Newmarket.
OL,12,FJones, from Oxford, visited the palace
OL,13,Ftwice before the theft, but denied
OL,14,Fthese were reconnaissance trips.
OL,16,FHe told jurors he "took advantage of"
OL,17,Fthe gold toilet's "facilities" while
OL,18,Fat the country house the day before it
OL,19,Fwas taken.
