OL,3,CTwo men to be sentenced over #4.75
OL,4,Cmillion gold toilet heist
OL,6,FAsked what it was like, Jones said:
OL,7,F"Splendid."
OL,9,FJones had worked as a roofer and
OL,10,Fbuilder for Sheen from about 2018 and
OL,11,Fwas effectively Sheen's "right-hand
OL,12,Fman", being trusted to arrange
OL,13,Fpayments for his friend's other
OL,14,Femployees.
OL,16,FHe was arrested on October 16 2019 and
OL,17,Fpolice analysed his phone. He had been
OL,18,Fsearching for newspaper reports about
OL,19,Fthe stolen toilet on September 20, the
OL,20,Ftrial heard.
