OL,6,FFrederick Doe, 37, also known as
OL,7,FFrederick Sines, of Winkfield,
OL,8,FWindsor, Berkshire, was found guilty
OL,9,Fof conspiracy to transfer criminal
OL,10,Fproperty.
OL,12,FHe walked free from court last month
OL,13,Fafter being given a suspended sentence
OL,14,Ffor his part in the heist.
OL,16,FDoe helped Sheen sell some of the gold
OL,17,Fin the following weeks, the court
OL,18,Fheard.
OL,20,FBora Guccuk, 41, from west London, was
OL,21,Fcleared of the same charge.
